    FROM [Questions] AS [c.Questions1]
    LEFT JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [q.User1] ON [c.Questions1].[UserId] = [q.User1].[Id]

        FROM [Categories] AS [c2]
        WHERE [c2].[CategoryId] = @__id_0
        ORDER BY [c2].[CategoryId]
    ) AS [t2] ON [c.Questions1].[CategoryId] = [t2].[CategoryId]
) AS [t3] ON [c.Questions.Answers].[QuestionId] = [t3].[QuestionId]
ORDER BY [t3].[CategoryId], [t3].[QuestionId], [c.Questions.Answers].[AnswerId]" (0723d8ff)

    FROM [Answers] AS [c.Questions.Answers0]
    INNER JOIN (

        FROM [Questions] AS [c.Questions2]
        LEFT JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [q.User2] ON [c.Questions2].[UserId] = [q.User2].[Id]
